sequenceDiagram
    participant Onboarding Application 
    participant Kafka
    participant TaskAggregator/TaskNotify
    participant EnrichmentUnit as Enrichment Unit (Quantum/CFR/STAM/Others)
    participant ConcertService
    participant Pipeline
    participant TaskStore as TaskStore Mongo Collection
    participant WorkflowStore as WorkflowView Mongo Collection
    participant LiveQuery
    participant AD Desktop UI 
    participant Encore Service  
    participant AO Dashboard 
    actor Advisor 



    Onboarding Application->> Kafka : Generate task data
    Kafka->>TaskAggregator/TaskNotify: Send task data
    TaskAggregator/TaskNotify->>EnrichmentUnit: Push task data/ fetch task Data for taskId
    TaskAggregator/TaskNotify->>TaskStore: Store task info
    EnrichmentUnit->>ConcertService: Enrich task events
    ConcertService->>WorkflowStore: Trigger event handler/Push task data to pipeline/(Store transformed/enriched task)
    LiveQuery->>Encore Service: Query for live data
    AD Desktop UI ->>LiveQuery: Display task/workflow
    Encore Service->>WorkflowStore : fetch onbaording task
    AO Dashboard ->> Encore Service : Display AO task/workflow
    Advisor->>AO Dashboard :Advisor can we view/refresh  task 
   Advisor->>AO Dashboard: Take action on task (e.g., Approve / Reject)
   AO Dashboard->>Encore Service: Send action event
   Encore Service->>Onboarding Application: Send task action update back to onboarding system
